Package: pbvar
Title: Bayesian Panel VAR Estimation with Hierarchical Priors
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Federica", "Ursillo", "federica.ursillo@studenti.unipd.it", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("NOME", "COGNOME", role = "ctb"
Description: Tools to estimate Bayesian panel vector autoregressions (PBVAR)
    using hierarchical priors and MCMC sampling. The package includes functions
    for posterior summaries and impulse response functions at global level, plus an example G7 panel dataset.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
